{"tid":2407740,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★施麗珊：建議內地取消隔離措施，以照顧居於內地的父母及滯留子女","createTime":"2021-02-14T09:54:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-15T04:28:01.000Z","uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":54,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"c36bad0230b15cab157649822e82f12de8634b2b","tid":2407740,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-14T09:54:19.000Z","msg":"香港社區組織協會去年12月以問卷訪問該會服務的基層家庭，共388人受訪，當中近七成受訪者稱，因不能頻繁往返兩地，難以照顧居於內地的父母。另有受訪者的年幼子女，受訪者因工作無法抽身接子女回港。<br />\n<br />\n社協幹事施麗珊表示，建議除了「回港易」豁免內地返港本地居民隔離檢疫，內地亦可<span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>取消有關隔離措施</strong></span>，設立兩地認可的健康碼，或縮短隔離期至一或三日，以方便兩地走的居民。她亦期望，隨着本港檢測能力增長，有關費用可下調。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20210214/s00001/1613284955248/%E6%96%B0%E5%86%A0%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E4%B8%AD%E6%B8%AF%E5%85%A9%E9%82%8A%E8%B5%B0%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E7%96%AB%E4%B8%8B%E5%8F%97%E5%BD%B1%E9%9F%BF-%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%94%E5%80%A1%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E4%BB%A3%E9%9A%94%E9%9B%A2-%E6%B8%9B%E6%AA%A2%E6%B8%AC%E8%B2%BB%E7%94%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210214%2Fs00001%2F1613284955248%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%2582%258A%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25BA%25AD%25E7%2596%25AB%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258F%2597%25E5%25BD%25B1%25E9%259F%25BF-%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2594%25E5%2580%25A1%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E9%259A%2594%25E9%259B%25A2-%25E6%25B8%259B%25E6%25AA%25A2%25E6%25B8%25AC%25E8%25B2%25BB%25E7%2594%25A8&d=kmAW5qHYNhnz24jV18NLuQqYqcROYCvJBJmaWwU8HGA%3D&h=f768322e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20210214%2Fs00001%2F1613284955248%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E5%2586%25A0%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%2582%258A%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E5%25AE%25B6